# backend/ — FastAPI Backend
# format: ctx/1.0
# last-verified: 2026-03-28
# edges: -> call/render | ~> subscribe/read

## Root — Entry Points
  main.py : Brand assistant server :8000 [root] @entry
    -> config.py, routers, services
  serve_game.py : Game engine server :8080 [root] @entry
    -> config.py, routers, services, templates
    ~> FunctionGemma
  config.py : Paths, keys, brand prompt [config]
  requirements.txt : Core Python deps [config]

## Subfolders
  data : 40 files — KG builders, datasets, DBs [dir]
  persona : 9 files — 4D dimension computers [dir]
  routers : 10 files — API route handlers [dir]
    -> services
  services : 22 files — Business logic [dir]
    -> data, persona
    ~> GeminiAPI, ICD11, TermuxAPI
  templates : 1 file — Game client SPA [dir]
  tests : 14 files — Test suite [dir]
    ~> services, routers

## External
  GeminiAPI : Gemini API — LLM inference [ext]
  ICD11 : WHO ICD-11 — Clinical classification [ext]
  TermuxAPI : termux-api — Android system access [ext]
  FunctionGemma : FunctionGemma — On-device function calling [ext]
